Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:34.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was my father's friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why didn't you take the dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I had a feeling if I took the dragon,\Nyou would've checkmated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it looked like\NI could checkmate you from the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought\Nyou would go for the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't play like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You came to checkmate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though he was my father's friend,\Nevery time he came over,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would get happy and restless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kouda, sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An emergency came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's fine. I was playing with Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Huh, how did it go?\N- Oh, I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apparently, a while ago, he and my father\Nwere members together in the federation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei made an interesting move just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It reminded me of the kind of moves\Nyou used to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- It looks like he's been studying quite a bit.\N- Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shogi wasn't my favorite, but it was precious\Ntime that I could spend with my busy father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I did my best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}For me, I wish he'd play a little more outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but I guess he's like me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the neighborhood and at school,\NI got bullied a lot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just couldn't seem to make any friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The kids in my class\Nwould have bewildering conversations...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I couldn't keep up with it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seemed like a foreign language.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet, the words he said\Nwhile on the other side of the shogi board{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}always made a deep impression on me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though he's an adult,\Nhe really spoke to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understood that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was the only person\Noutside of my family who did that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Modern Shogi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up Momo from kindergarten?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The thing is, my aunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you've met her before, right?\NShe's the proprietress of the club I work at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She made a misstep while going down stairs\Nand hurt her foot. I'm at the hospital now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hina isn't picking up because she's at her\Nschool club, and Grandpa is busy at the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Would you do me this favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo, time to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}It seems she's having fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo, what song is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's the cat song! Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo's hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. A little more\Nand it would've fallen into the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A cute girl! Let's play!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I like her! I like her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, come on, little one, let's play!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, come on, let's play!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SLAM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huff\NHuff
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.01,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wag\NWag\NWag
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo, are you okay?\NDid you hit your forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I made her cry. I'm sorry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sadness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Look, we're home, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's tend to those scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Momo, do you know where the first-aid kit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sand got into the scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Here, rinse your hand off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rei, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sorry. Hang in there a little longer, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, first...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Disinfectant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That and gauze...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, children often fall down,\Nso you don't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo doesn't hurt anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}So bright...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Um, I'm thirsty, so can I get some milk maybe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rei really felt bad about that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He hardly ate anything at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Momo, you probably cried too much\Nand made him worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Momo didn't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't had dinner yet-meow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Big
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Big Liars
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Rei was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big tears drip-dripped down his cheeks.\NMomo saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why was Rei crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm sure it's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...he remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rei also had...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...a little sister, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day, my normal life suddenly ended,\Nas if it had been ripped away from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:11:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}When I returned from the school trip,\Nmy precious father, mother, and little sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...had become cold, stiff, spotted masses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They said it was an involvement\Nwith a drunken truck driver...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apparently, the three of them\Nwere killed instantly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what will happen to their son.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The younger sister, Kiwako,\Nwill probably take him in, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way that woman would agree to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And his grandfather is far too old...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You fool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going to happen to the hospital?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You finally gave up shogi\Nand agreed to take over after I retired.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- I thought everything would turn out well...\N- Father-in-law, it'll be okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've got me. I'll take care of everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, that's what I've been saying\Nfrom the beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you only thought about big brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Poor child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I'll find a good orphanage for Rei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I didn't know what an orphanage was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koud—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...until then, no matter how tough school was,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in the evening I could return\Nto my warm room and relax safely by myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I go there, even though I went back\Nto my room, somebody would always be there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somebody would be there\Nwhen I went to sleep, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I realized out of the 365 days in a year,\NI wouldn't have a single moment to feel relief.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then he arrived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Many of my blood relatives\Nhad come to the funeral,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but out of everyone in the room,\Nhe was the only one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...who made me feel so nostalgic\Nthat I wanted to cry out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like I said, my husband will be taking over the\NKiriyama Hospital. There's nothing else to say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe Kiwako's terrible attitude.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's always been like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- Shhh, we're in front of the deceased.\N- But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...like shogi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was the moment of an agreement.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The god of shogi and I\Nwere bound to each other by an ugly lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a lie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first time in my life\Nthat I lied in order to live...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, I could never return.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, the ropes were cut\Nand the curtain dropped,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I became the child of a shogi family.{\i0}
